{"word":"G2766 - κέραμος - kéramos - ker'-am-os - Tiling","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κέραμος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kéramos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>ker'-am-os"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Tiling"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"தட்டோடு - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. clay, potter's earth"},{"paragraph":"2. anything made of clay, earthen ware"},{"paragraph":"3. a (roofing) tile the roof itself"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Probably from the base of <a href=\"#/G2767 - κεράννυμι - keránnymi - ker-an'-noo-mee/2767\">G2767</a> (through the idea of <i>mixing</i> clay and water); <i>earthenware</i>, that is, a <i>tile</i> (by analogy a thin <i>roof</i> or <i>awning</i>): - tiling."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2763 - κεραμεύς - kerameús - ker-am-yooce'/2763\">G2763</a>, <a href=\"#/G2764 - κεραμικός - keramikós - ker-am-ik-os'/2764\">G2764</a>, <a href=\"#/G2765 - κεράμιον - kerámion - ker-am'-ee-on/2765\">G2765</a>, <a href=\"#/G2766 - κέραμος - kéramos - ker'-am-os/2766\">G2766</a>"}]}